data.description: Rarely available income producing duplex or fabulous set up for extended family, this duplex sits at the intersection of two canals in Cape Coral. The spectacular views from the pool area and fenced back yard showcase canal living at its' finest.  The front yard is home to a beautiful mature mango tree, which will provide plentiful fruit for you and your friends!  The sounds and views of nature abound in this unique property. This home provides quick access to all the restaurants and shopping in downtown Cape Coral, and up and coming Bimini Basin area, yet a private enclave to enjoy all that SW Florida has to offer. Unit 1 has 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom. The light colors and open floor plan gives this unit a delightful feeling. Unit 2 has one bedroom plus den, updated kitchen and a bathroom. Both units have their own laundry and the pool and lanai extend throughout the back of the property. Carport, parking pad and oversized corner lot complete this amazing property.
